OL,3,CTeaser trailer released for return of
OL,4,CChannel Island show Bergerac
OL,6,FA new teaser trailer has been released
OL,7,Fas Bergerac takes another step closer
OL,8,Fto his return to Jersey.
OL,10,FThe teaser shows a sneak peek of
OL,11,FDamien Molony playing the iconic role
OL,12,Fof Jim Bergerac.
OL,14,FThe six-part series was produced by
OL,15,FBlacklight TV, Jersey-based Westward
OL,16,FStudios and was supported by Visit
OL,17,FJersey.
OL,19,FFilming took place in August and
OL,20,FSeptember in Jersey and later in Devon.
