OL,4,CChannel Island show Bergerac
OL,6,FZoe Wanamaker will also star as
OL,7,FCharlie Hungerford - Bergerac's mother-
OL,8,Fin-law - as well as Chloe Sweetlove
OL,9,Fwho will play Jim's daughter, Kim.
OL,11,FThe series reimagines 1980s drama
OL,12,Fwhich starred John Nettles for nine
OL,13,Fseasons.
OL,15,FThe new series will follow one
OL,16,Fcharacter-led murder across all six
OL,17,Fone-hour episodes, rather than telling
OL,18,Fa new storyline each episode.
OL,20,FUKTV will release Bergerac on U and
OL,21,FU&DRAMA in February 2025.
